{"data":{"featured":{"edges":[{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Surftech Adaptive Security Roadmap","cover":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/png;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/7696692bc303d1912f056bac49dc3e76/18b2e/asr.png","srcSet":"/static/7696692bc303d1912f056bac49dc3e76/df062/asr.png 175w,\n/static/7696692bc303d1912f056bac49dc3e76/d8f52/asr.png 350w,\n/static/7696692bc303d1912f056bac49dc3e76/18b2e/asr.png 700w,\n/static/7696692bc303d1912f056bac49dc3e76/9f7a3/asr.png 1400w","sizes":"(min-width: 700px) 700px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/7696692bc303d1912f056bac49dc3e76/2eb69/asr.avif 175w,\n/static/7696692bc303d1912f056bac49dc3e76/46c45/asr.avif 350w,\n/static/7696692bc303d1912f056bac49dc3e76/12925/asr.avif 700w,\n/static/7696692bc303d1912f056bac49dc3e76/da5e1/asr.avif 1400w","type":"image/avif","sizes":"(min-width: 700px) 700px, 100vw"},{"srcSet":"/static/7696692bc303d1912f056bac49dc3e76/ff6f3/asr.webp 175w,\n/static/7696692bc303d1912f056bac49dc3e76/a4795/asr.webp 350w,\n/static/7696692bc303d1912f056bac49dc3e76/377b6/asr.webp 700w,\n/static/7696692bc303d1912f056bac49dc3e76/c0cfd/asr.webp 1400w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 700px) 700px, 100vw"}]},"width":700,"height":350}}},"tech":["PowerBI","Excel","Python","Markdown"],"github":null,"external":"https://www.surftech.it/adaptive-security-roadmap/?section=patrimonio&subSection=framework","cta":"https://www.surftech.it/adaptive-security-roadmap/?section=patrimonio&subSection=framework"},"html":"<p>The <strong>Adaptive Security Roadmap</strong> collects and categorizes the security measures already in place according to best practice guidelines based on the international <a href=\"https://www.cisecurity.org/controls\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">CIS Controls® standard</a>. The results are analyzed using a custom-built application, which generates a tailored Security Improvement Plan aligned with business requirements, existing investments, available technical resources, and budget constraints.</p>\n<p>Throughout the contractual period, clients also gain access to an exclusive platform that allows continuous monitoring of their security posture and the progress of all improvement activities.</p>"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Mail Authentication Analyzer","cover":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/png;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/99c6bd98b1d6f2675a882c622dfb2b82/2d639/auth.png","srcSet":"/static/99c6bd98b1d6f2675a882c622dfb2b82/a3bf4/auth.png 175w,\n/static/99c6bd98b1d6f2675a882c622dfb2b82/4fe50/auth.png 350w,\n/static/99c6bd98b1d6f2675a882c622dfb2b82/2d639/auth.png 700w","sizes":"(min-width: 700px) 700px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/99c6bd98b1d6f2675a882c622dfb2b82/7f040/auth.avif 175w,\n/static/99c6bd98b1d6f2675a882c622dfb2b82/ab73a/auth.avif 350w,\n/static/99c6bd98b1d6f2675a882c622dfb2b82/ee81d/auth.avif 700w","type":"image/avif","sizes":"(min-width: 700px) 700px, 100vw"},{"srcSet":"/static/99c6bd98b1d6f2675a882c622dfb2b82/ee308/auth.webp 175w,\n/static/99c6bd98b1d6f2675a882c622dfb2b82/68e05/auth.webp 350w,\n/static/99c6bd98b1d6f2675a882c622dfb2b82/ed668/auth.webp 700w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 700px) 700px, 100vw"}]},"width":700,"height":432}}},"tech":["Python","DMARC","DKIM","SPF","Markdown"],"github":null,"external":null,"cta":null},"html":"<p>Developed a Python script designed to analyze domain security configurations by querying public DNS servers. Starting from a list of domains, the script retrieves all relevant DNS records related to security settings.</p>\n<p>It then generates a comprehensive report in Markdown and PDF formats, highlighting both critical issues and strengths in each domain’s configuration.</p>\n<p>The script supports multiple input modes:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>A list of domains from a file</li>\n<li>Single domain input</li>\n<li>Email files for analyzing message headers</li>\n</ul>"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"MFA Implementation Analyzer","cover":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/png;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/9c4bd1b0f2a94251467b97fbba1dd8a6/4e258/mfa.png","srcSet":"/static/9c4bd1b0f2a94251467b97fbba1dd8a6/68202/mfa.png 175w,\n/static/9c4bd1b0f2a94251467b97fbba1dd8a6/fe25d/mfa.png 350w,\n/static/9c4bd1b0f2a94251467b97fbba1dd8a6/4e258/mfa.png 700w","sizes":"(min-width: 700px) 700px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/9c4bd1b0f2a94251467b97fbba1dd8a6/1934d/mfa.avif 175w,\n/static/9c4bd1b0f2a94251467b97fbba1dd8a6/8f8aa/mfa.avif 350w,\n/static/9c4bd1b0f2a94251467b97fbba1dd8a6/a273d/mfa.avif 700w","type":"image/avif","sizes":"(min-width: 700px) 700px, 100vw"},{"srcSet":"/static/9c4bd1b0f2a94251467b97fbba1dd8a6/745fa/mfa.webp 175w,\n/static/9c4bd1b0f2a94251467b97fbba1dd8a6/b0f73/mfa.webp 350w,\n/static/9c4bd1b0f2a94251467b97fbba1dd8a6/dcd92/mfa.webp 700w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 700px) 700px, 100vw"}]},"width":700,"height":400}}},"tech":["MicrosoftGraph","Python","JSON","PowerBI"],"github":null,"external":null,"cta":null},"html":"<p>Developed a script designed to assess the level of Multi-Factor Authentication (MFA) adoption across a Microsoft 365 tenant — a process often complicated by missing licenses or inactive services. The script collects essential identity and authentication data, which is then visualized through a custom Power BI dashboard.</p>\n<p>The dashboard enables rich filtering and interactive selections to identify key gaps in security, including a complete list of users without MFA enabled.</p>\n<p>Prebuilt reports include: Administrators without MFA, Active mailbox accounts without MFA, Member and guest users lacking, Self-Service Password Reset (SSPR) configuration, Dormant or inactive user accounts.</p>"}}]}}}